with version stable 2.6
with base    perl
with role    dictionary
with trait   console
with source  $SOURCEFORGE_URL edictionary/edict/edict-$VERSION/edict-$VERSION.tar.gz
with info    good 20120606
with info    last 20100625
with info    home http://edictionary.sourceforge.net/
with info    docs http://edictionary.sourceforge.net/doc.php
with info    freecode edictionary
with info    cite 'English command line dictionary and thesaurus
Edict can be used to view the meaning of English words.
It can also provide related details like etymology,
function, pronunciation etc.
Adding support for other languages is not included, but is easy.
Edict can grab the meaning of any word 
from the convenience of the command line.
You can ask for meanings of multiple words at once.
You can call edict from within your scripts.'

build(){ make install prefix=$DESTDIR/usr/bin; }
